<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC5">
<l>nampiṉēṉ piṟār naṉporuḷtaṉṉaiyum</l>
<l>nampiṉēṉ maṭavāraiyum muṉ elām</l>
<l>cempoṉ māṭat tiruk kurukūr nampik</l>
<l>kaṉpaṉāy aṭiyēṉ catirttēṉ iṉṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Always before, I coveted the good things of others,</l>
<l>I coveted women.</l>
<l>Today, I, your slave, have been blessed [to] become the devotee</l>
<l>of the Lord of red-gold mansioned holy Kurukūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
